      tagline: 'La belleza del mundo natural',
      copy: 'Nuestra fotografía de paisaje y naturaleza es ideal para campañas, turismo, uso editorial y proyectos de narrativa visual.',
      perfectFor: 'Marcas de viaje, campañas ambientales, proyectos editoriales',
      includes: 'Fotografía en locación, luz natural, edición avanzada',
      img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05?w=1400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop',
      alt: 'Paisaje natural de montañas al amanecer',
    },
  ],
  bandTitle: '¿Buscas elevar tu marca con visuales de alta calidad?',
  bandCopy: 'Planifiquemos tu próxima producción.',
  bandCta: 'Enviar un brief',
  bandCall: 'Llamar (786) 763-2091',
  formEyebrow: 'Brief de proyecto',
  formTitle: 'Cuéntanos tu proyecto.',
  formLede: 'Comparte lo esencial — qué necesitas, cuándo y dónde. Respondemos en un día hábil con disponibilidad y propuesta.',
  formName: 'Nombre completo',
  formCompany: 'Empresa',
  formEmail: 'Email',
  formPhone: 'Teléfono',
  formService: 'Tipo de servicio',
  formServiceOptions: [
    'Fotografía gastronómica y de restaurantes',
    'Fotografía de producto',
    'Retratos profesionales',
    'Cobertura de eventos',
    'Fotografía de naturaleza y paisaje',
  ],
  formDate: 'Fecha tentativa',
  formLocation: 'Locación',
  formLocationPh: 'Ciudad, estudio, locación...',
  formBudget: 'Rango de presupuesto',
  formBudgetOptions: ['Menos de $1,000', '$1,000 – $2,500', '$2,500 – $5,000', 'Más de $5,000', 'Aún no lo sé'],
  formBrief: 'Brief del proyecto',
  formBriefPh: 'Cuéntanos qué quieres lograr, entregables, referencias, plazos...',
  formSubmit: 'Enviar brief',
  formNote: 'Respondemos en un día hábil. Sin compromiso.',
  formSuccess: 'Brief recibido. Te contactamos en un día hábil con disponibilidad y propuesta.',
} : {
  title: 'Photo & Video Productions in Miami | Miami Photography Center',
  description: 'Creative visual services for brands, businesses, and professionals in Miami. Food & restaurant photography, product photography, professional portraits, event coverage, and nature photography.',
  breadcrumbHome: 'Home',
  breadcrumbServices: 'Services',
  breadcrumbCurrent: 'Productions',
  heroEyebrow: 'Productions',
  heroTitle: 'Photo & Video Productions.',
  heroLede: 'Creative Visual Services for Brands, Businesses & Professionals.',
  heroCta1: 'Plan Your Production',
  heroCta2: 'See the services',
  servicesEyebrow: 'Featured production services',
  servicesTitle: 'Five specialties.<br/>One standard of craft.',
  perfectFor: 'Perfect for',
  includes: 'Includes',
  services: [
    {
      num: '01',
      title: 'Food & Restaurant Photography',
      tagline: 'Delicious visuals that attract attention',
      copy: 'We photograph dishes to enhance their appeal through expert lighting and styling. Ideal for menus, social media, food delivery apps, and restaurant marketing campaigns.',
      perfectFor: 'Restaurants, food trucks, catering services',
      includes: 'On-location photography, styled shots, high-resolution editing',
      img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1414235077428-338989a2e8c0?w=1400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop',
      alt: 'Gourmet dish plated at a restaurant with careful lighting',
    },
    {
      num: '02',
      title: 'Product Photography',
      tagline: 'Clean, detailed visuals that sell',
      copy: 'High-resolution product photography for eCommerce, advertising, and catalogs. We highlight the form, function, and aesthetic of each item with clean, detailed visuals.',
      perfectFor: 'Online stores, Amazon sellers, marketing agencies',
      includes: 'Studio lighting, white backgrounds, creative setups, editing',
      img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523275335684-37898b6baf30?w=1400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop',
      alt: 'Product photograph of a watch on a clean background',
    },
    {
      num: '03',
      title: 'Professional Portraits',
      tagline: 'Headshots and personal branding with character',
      copy: 'We create corporate headshots, personal branding portraits, and editorial-style images with a focus on professionalism and individuality.',
      perfectFor: 'Executives, freelancers, actors, influencers',
      includes: 'Lighting setup, background options, retouching',
      img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=1400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop',
      alt: 'Professional portrait of a man in natural light',
    },
    {
      num: '04',
      title: 'Event Coverage',
      tagline: 'Capture every moment with clarity and class',
      copy: 'From conferences to private celebrations, our event photography captures real moments and key highlights with elegance.',
      perfectFor: 'Corporate events, weddings, quinceañeras, galas',
      includes: 'Full-event coverage, candid & posed photos, digital delivery',
      img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511578314322-379afb476865?w=1400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop',
      alt: 'Event venue lit up during a celebration',
    },
    {
      num: '05',
      title: 'Nature & Landscape Photography',
      tagline: 'Capture the beauty of the natural world',
      copy: 'Our landscape and nature photography is ideal for campaigns, tourism, editorial use, and visual storytelling projects.',
      perfectFor: 'Travel brands, environmental campaigns, editorial projects',
      includes: 'On-location photography, natural light, advanced editing',
      img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05?w=1400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop',
      alt: 'Natural mountain landscape at sunrise',
    },
  ],
  bandTitle: 'Looking to elevate your brand with high-quality visuals?',
  bandCopy: 'Let’s plan your next production.',
  bandCta: 'Send a Brief',
  bandCall: 'Call (786) 763-2091',
  formEyebrow: 'Project brief',
  formTitle: 'Tell us about your project.',
  formLede: 'Share the essentials — what you need, when, and where. We respond within one business day with availability and a proposal.',
  formName: 'Full name',
  formCompany: 'Company',
  formEmail: 'Email',
  formPhone: 'Phone',
  formService: 'Service type',
  formServiceOptions: [
    'Food & restaurant photography',
    'Product photography',
    'Professional portraits',
    'Event coverage',
    'Nature & landscape photography',
  ],
  formDate: 'Tentative date',
  formLocation: 'Location',
  formLocationPh: 'City, studio, venue...',
  formBudget: 'Budget range',
  formBudgetOptions: ['Under $1,000', '$1,000 – $2,500', '$2,500 – $5,000', '$5,000+', 'Not sure yet'],
  formBrief: 'Project brief',
  formBriefPh: 'Tell us what you want to achieve, deliverables, references, deadlines...',
  formSubmit: 'Send Brief',
  formNote: 'We respond within one business day. No commitment.',
  formSuccess: 'Brief received. We’ll contact you within one business day with availability and a proposal.',
};

const serviceSchema = JSON.stringify({
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Photo & Video Productions',
  serviceType: 'Photography and video production services',
  description: 'Food & restaurant photography, product photography, professional portraits, event coverage, and nature & landscape photography for brands, businesses, and professionals.',
  provider: {
    '@type': 'LocalBusiness',
    name: 'Miami Photography Center',
    telephone: '+1-786-763-2091',
    address: { '@type': 'PostalAddress', streetAddress: '3911 SW 27th St', addressLocality: 'West Park', addressRegion: 'FL', postalCode: '33023', addressCountry: 'US' },
  },
  areaServed: 'South Florida',
});
---
<Base locale={locale} title={t.title} description={t.description}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={serviceSchema} slot="head" is:inline />

  <!-- ==================== PAGE HERO ==================== -->
  <header class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__inner">
      <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href={p('/')}>{t.breadcrumbHome}</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href={p('/services')}>{t.breadcrumbServices}</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span aria-current="page">{t.breadcrumbCurrent}</span>
      </nav>
      <p class="eyebrow" data-anim="fade-up">{t.heroEyebrow}</p>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title" data-anim="fade-up">{t.heroTitle}</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__lede" data-anim="fade-up">{t.heroLede}</p>
      <div class="prods-hero__ctas" data-anim="fade-up">
        <a href="#production-form" class="btn btn--primary">{t.heroCta1}</a>
        <a href="#prods-services" class="btn btn--ghost">{t.heroCta2} <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ==================== 5 SERVICES — ALTERNATING ROWS ==================== -->
  <section id="prods-services" class="prods-services" aria-labelledby="prods-services-title">
    <div class="prods-services__head">
      <p class="eyebrow">{t.servicesEyebrow}</p>
      <h2 id="prods-services-title" class="prods-services__title" set:html={t.servicesTitle} />
    </div>
    <div class="prods-rows">
      {t.services.map((service, i) => (
        <article class={`prods-row${i % 2 === 1 ? ' prods-row--flip' : ''}`}>
          <div class="prods-row__media" data-anim="fade-up">
            <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src={service.img} alt={service.alt} width="1400" height="1050" />
          </div>
          <div class="prods-row__body" data-anim="fade-up">
            <span class="prods-row__num">{service.num}</span>
            <h3 class="prods-row__title">{service.title}</h3>
            <p class="prods-row__tagline">{service.tagline}</p>
            <p class="prods-row__copy">{service.copy}</p>
            <dl class="prods-row__meta">
              <div>
                <dt>{t.perfectFor}</dt>
                <dd>{service.perfectFor}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt>{t.includes}</dt>
                <dd>{service.includes}</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== BIG CTA BAND ==================== -->
  <section class="cta" aria-labelledby="prods-band-title">
    <div class="cta__inner">
      <h2 id="prods-band-title" class="cta__title">{t.bandTitle}</h2>
      <p class="cta__copy">{t.bandCopy}</p>
      <div class="cta__actions">
        <a href="#production-form" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">{t.bandCta}</a>
        <a href="tel:+17867632091" class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg">{t.bandCall}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== BRIEF FORM ==================== -->
  <section class="prods-form" aria-labelledby="prods-form-title">
    <div class="prods-form__inner">
      <div class="prods-form__intro">
        <p class="eyebrow">{t.formEyebrow}</p>
        <h2 id="prods-form-title" class="prods-form__title">{t.formTitle}</h2>
        <p class="prods-form__lede">{t.formLede}</p>
      </div>
      <form id="production-form" class="form js-demo-form" action="#" method="POST" data-success={t.formSuccess}>
        <div class="form__row">
          <div class="form__field">
            <label for="pf-name">{t.formName} *</label>
            <input id="pf-name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form__field">
            <label for="pf-company">{t.formCompany}</label>
            <input id="pf-company" name="company" type="text" autocomplete="organization" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form__row">
          <div class="form__field">
            <label for="pf-email">{t.formEmail} *</label>
            <input id="pf-email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form__field">
            <label for="pf-phone">{t.formPhone}</label>
            <input id="pf-phone" name="phone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form__row">
          <div class="form__field">
            <label for="pf-service">{t.formService}</label>
            <select id="pf-service" name="service">
              {t.formServiceOptions.map((opt) => <option value={opt}>{opt}</option>)}
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form__field">
            <label for="pf-date">{t.formDate}</label>
            <input id="pf-date" name="date" type="date" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form__row">
          <div class="form__field">
            <label for="pf-location">{t.formLocation}</label>
            <input id="pf-location" name="location" type="text" placeholder={t.formLocationPh} />
          </div>
          <div class="form__field">
            <label for="pf-budget">{t.formBudget}</label>
            <select id="pf-budget" name="budget">
              {t.formBudgetOptions.map((opt) => <option value={opt}>{opt}</option>)}
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form__field">
          <label for="pf-brief">{t.formBrief}</label>
          <textarea id="pf-brief" name="brief" placeholder={t.formBriefPh}></textarea>
        </div>
        <div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">{t.formSubmit}</button>
        </div>
        <p class="form__note">{t.formNote}</p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style is:global>
/* ============================================================
   PRODUCTIONS PAGE (.prods-)
   ============================================================ */
.prods-hero__ctas {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 14px;
}

/* Services — alternating rows */
.prods-services {
  padding: var(--section-gap) var(--gutter);
  background: var(--color-pure-white);
}
.prods-services__head {
  max-width: var(--page-max);
  margin: 0 auto 70px;
}
.prods-services__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 72px);
  line-height: 1.07;
  letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  max-width: 22ch;
}
.prods-rows {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: clamp(60px, 8vw, 110px);
  max-width: var(--page-max);
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.prods-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: clamp(30px, 4.5vw, 70px);
  align-items: center;
}
.prods-row__media {
  border-radius: var(--r-card);
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--color-ash);
}
.prods-row__media img {
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform .8s var(--ease-out);
}
.prods-row:hover .prods-row__media img { transform: scale(1.04); }
.prods-row--flip .prods-row__media { order: 2; }
.prods-row__num {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 17px;
  color: var(--color-electric-blue);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.prods-row__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 44px);
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  color: var(--color-apple-ink);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.prods-row__tagline {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18px;
  letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  color: var(--color-graphite);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.prods-row__copy {
  font-size: 17px;
  color: var(--color-graphite);
  line-height: 1.55;
  max-width: 52ch;
  margin-bottom: 26px;
}
.prods-row__meta {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
  margin: 0;
}
.prods-row__meta > div {
  background: var(--color-fog-canvas);
  border-radius: 18px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
}
.prods-row__meta dt {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--color-electric-blue);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.prods-row__meta dd {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--color-charcoal);
  line-height: 1.5;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .prods-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .prods-row--flip .prods-row__media { order: 0; }
}

/* Brief form */
.prods-form {
  padding: var(--section-gap) var(--gutter);
  background: var(--color-fog-canvas);
}
.prods-form__inner {
  max-width: var(--page-max);
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
  gap: clamp(36px, 5vw, 80px);
  align-items: start;
}
.prods-form__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 60px);
  line-height: 1.07;
  letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.prods-form__lede {
  font-size: 17px;
  color: var(--color-graphite);
  line-height: 1.5;
  max-width: 44ch;
}
.prods-form .form {
  background: var(--color-pure-white);
  border-radius: var(--r-card);
  padding: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 44px);
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .prods-form__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
